description	"Sith Trooper

^2Weaponry:
- Sith Carbine (2)
-- Based on Clone Rifle
-- 15 Rapid Shot Burst
-- 50% Less DMG
-- Alt Reload
- 1 Concussion Grenade
- Short Sword
-- Yellow / Cyan Styles
-- 15% Faster Movement

^8Attributes:
- Close Combat Training (1)
- Reinforcements (2)
- Assemble (1)

The Sith Troopers were infantry units in the armed forces of the Sith Empire during the Jedi Civil War. Some ended up fighting on the Vaklu side in the Onderonian Civil War."